message.entry: Argument must be a structure, or a non-empty character vector or string scalar.
Format structure must contain a field named ''ext''.
All formats must specify at least one extension.
Format extensions must be a cell array of character vectors or string array.
Format {0} must be a character vector or string scalar containing the name of a valid non-empty function name or function handle, or empty.
Description in format {0} must be a character vector, string scalar or empty.
Alpha channel values must be scalar integers.
All alpha channel values must be scalar values of 0 or 1.
Input must be valid function handle or function name specified as character vector or a string scalar.
The extension ''{0}'' is already in the registry.
